<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 10:08:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解救人质是以色列的道义胜利，但哈马斯将很快适应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/hostage-rescue-is-a-moral-victory-for-israel-but-hamas-will-be-quick-to-adapt/0000018d-9c78-d92c-a9ed-fff99bbf0000</link><description>以色列已经制定了加沙救援行动计划，但由于保护人质的生命安全，大部分计划未能实施</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 09:40:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/hostage-rescue-is-a-moral-victory-for-israel-but-hamas-will-be-quick-to-adapt/0000018d-9c78-d92c-a9ed-fff99bbf0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡正在准备不在场证明，以维持哈马斯在加沙地带的统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-preparing-his-alibi-for-keeping-hamas-rule-in-the-gaza-strip/0000018d-99b8-db74-a1ef-dbfa42a20000</link><description>关于以色列国防军在拉法开展地面行动的声明，以及否认任何针对加沙的日后计划，可能会让总理指责美国未能履行其“全面战胜”哈马斯的承诺。仍然没有迹象表明以色列接近这一目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 03:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-preparing-his-alibi-for-keeping-hamas-rule-in-the-gaza-strip/0000018d-99b8-db74-a1ef-dbfa42a20000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙南部丧生；巴勒斯坦人称拉法袭击造成 48 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article-live/israeli-forces-rescue-two-hostages-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-9a62-d92c-a9ed-fbfb7e400006</link><description>以色列军队在拉法救出被哈马斯扣押的两名人质 ■ 两名来自马格兰突击队的以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带南部被杀 ■​​ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列对加沙地带的安全控制“在可预见的未来没有其他选择” ■ 拜登、内塔尼亚胡美国对以色列在加沙的军事行为发出警告 ■ 以色列国防军拉法地面入侵迫在眉睫，埃及威胁以色列和哈马斯</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 03:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article-live/israeli-forces-rescue-two-hostages-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-9a62-d92c-a9ed-fbfb7e400006</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙解救了被哈马斯囚禁的两名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-rescue-two-hostages-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-9b49-df62-a3fd-9fcd0a970000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，这两人分别是 70 岁的路易斯·诺伯托·哈尔 (Louis Norberto Har) 和 60 岁的费尔南多·马曼 (Fernando Marman)，他们于 10 月 7 日在尼尔·伊扎克基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Yitzhak) 被绑架，并被关押在拉法的一间公寓里。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 03:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-rescue-two-hostages-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-9b49-df62-a3fd-9fcd0a970000</guid></item><item><title>尽管信用评级被下调，以色列外长斯莫特里奇仍选择不与财政部高级官员会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-rating-downgrade-israeli-fm-smotrich-chooses-not-to-meet-with-top-treasury-staff/0000018d-9a34-dc01-a9cf-9a7dfb4d0000</link><description>相反，财政部长参加了对陆军朱利斯基地的参观。内塔尼亚胡迄今为止尚未宣布任何计划就评级行动进行讨论</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-rating-downgrade-israeli-fm-smotrich-chooses-not-to-meet-with-top-treasury-staff/0000018d-9a34-dc01-a9cf-9a7dfb4d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟将推进有争议的军队草案法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-to-advance-controversial-army-draft-bill/0000018d-99f7-dc01-a9cf-9bff1d670000</link><description>该法案可能会在大约两周内获得议会批准，旨在延长义务兵役和预备役兵役，并提高预备役军人的豁免年龄，但不会改变给予极端正统正统派男性的豁免年龄</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 22:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-to-advance-controversial-army-draft-bill/0000018d-99f7-dc01-a9cf-9bff1d670000</guid></item><item><title>拜登敦促内塔尼亚胡制定“可靠”计划，在以色列进攻之前保护拉法的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/biden-tells-netanyahu-israel-must-have-credible-plan-to-protect-palestinians-in-rafah/0000018d-99ae-dc01-a9cf-9befa6210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡指示以色列军队起草计划，在军事入侵之前疏散目前在拉法寻求庇护的近100万巴勒斯坦平民。两位领导人还讨论了与哈马斯达成人质协议的持续努力</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 21:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/biden-tells-netanyahu-israel-must-have-credible-plan-to-protect-palestinians-in-rafah/0000018d-99ae-dc01-a9cf-9befa6210000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨在民调中大幅领先内塔尼亚胡；目前的联盟面临失去多数席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/gantz-holds-wide-lead-over-netanyahu-in-polls-current-coalition-faces-majority-loss/0000018d-99ac-d92c-a9ed-fbfd78510000</link><description>在以色列新闻媒体进行的两次民意调查中，甘茨领导的民族团结党获得 37 个席位，内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团获得 18 个席位</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 21:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/gantz-holds-wide-lead-over-netanyahu-in-polls-current-coalition-faces-majority-loss/0000018d-99ac-d92c-a9ed-fbfd78510000</guid></item><item><title>法院在认罪协议中判定管道公司污染以色列自然保护区有罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/court-convicts-pipeline-company-in-plea-deal-for-polluting-israeli-nature-reserve/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfdc0510000</link><description>该公司和两名公司官员被判对造成“该国历史上最大的生态灾难之一”的石油泄漏负责。这些罪行可能会被判处最高三年的监禁，但协议要求仅处以罚款</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 19:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/court-convicts-pipeline-company-in-plea-deal-for-polluting-israeli-nature-reserve/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfdc0510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回允许在以色列国防军基地食用 Chametz 的请愿书，裁定侵犯权利“相当轻微”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-brushes-off-petition-to-allow-eating-chametz-on-idf-bases/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfd0e520000</link><description>法官们决定不干预以色列国防军的命令；判决强调军队承诺不搜查士兵的装备，这让请愿者感到“安慰”。他们说，“以色列国防军否认存在这些安排，但它们是请愿书的主要动机”</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-brushes-off-petition-to-allow-eating-chametz-on-idf-bases/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfd0e520000</guid></item><item><title>高风险：据报道摩洛哥大麻经销商抵制以色列，引用巴勒斯坦人的苦难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/high-stakes-moroccan-hashish-dealers-boycott-israel-citing-palestinian-suffering/0000018d-98dd-d92c-a9ed-fbfd9a030000</link><description>尽管向以色列出口大麻对摩洛哥的经销商来说利润丰厚，但他们不再愿意向以色列经销商出售大麻：“当我们的巴勒斯坦兄弟遭受饥饿时，为什么以色列人能够靠卖摩洛哥大麻谋生呢？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 18:56:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/high-stakes-moroccan-hashish-dealers-boycott-israel-citing-palestinian-suffering/0000018d-98dd-d92c-a9ed-fbfd9a030000</guid></item><item><title>拜登有一周的时间需要忘记，但内塔尼亚胡应该记住他的一些事情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/biden-had-a-week-to-forget-but-theres-something-netanyahu-should-remember-about-him/0000018d-98f5-dc01-a9cf-9afd98ef0000</link><description>美国媒体无视特朗普的失态和无知，却关注拜登的年龄和错误。因此，当美国总统称以色列在加沙的军事行动“太过分”时，许多人很快将其视为另一个错误。但拜登说出了他的真实想法</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 18:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/biden-had-a-week-to-forget-but-theres-something-netanyahu-should-remember-about-him/0000018d-98f5-dc01-a9cf-9afd98ef0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 128 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</link><description>据报道，埃及警告哈马斯，它有两周时间在以色列国防军拉法之前与以色列达成停火协议，但埃及还威胁称，如果以色列向以色列发动地面进攻，将暂停与以色列的和平条约。 哈马斯高级官员：对拉法的任何袭击都将结束人质谈判释放协议 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯飞往卡塔尔，与总理阿勒萨尼讨论战后加沙的前景 ■ 战争结束 128 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属向国际刑事法院提出针对哈马斯领导人的索赔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</link><description>已获释的人质以及仍被关押在加沙的人质亲属将飞往海牙，在国际刑事法院提供此案证词，该法院部分寻求对哈马斯领导人发出逮捕令</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:15:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者建立西岸前哨基地；其他人在另一起事件中袭击巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</link><description>以色列国防消息人士怀疑政府是否会撤离建在国家控制土地上的前哨基地 ■ 大约 15 名以色列人袭击了西岸北部的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长：政府有关国内问题的决定非法通过，必须重新考虑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</link><description>几项政府私营部门决议的通过没有适当的专业和法律基础，甚至存在法律障碍。代表总检察长发出的一封信命令政府在额外审议中重新考虑这些问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列指控哈马斯关系后，约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人担心近东救济工程处关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</link><description>该联合国机构为约旦河西岸约 87 万巴勒斯坦人提供服务，运营着 96 所学校和 43 个初级医疗机构。巴勒斯坦人担心如果该机构的资金不恢复将会发生什么</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:50:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝哈马斯，针对犹太人：在埃尔多安的土耳其，加沙战争营造了一种危险的气氛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日大屠杀以来，土耳其发生了一系列反以色列抗议和事件，这些抗议和事件有时不符合逻辑，但显然是受到总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 信息的启发</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的经济表现相当不错。那么，是什么在吞噬穆迪呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</link><description>穆迪下调以色列信用评级的原因只有一件事：不确定性 — — 而不仅仅是加沙战争的不确定性。政府的反应不是倾听，而是愤怒和空洞的保证</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:44:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将在超级碗期间投放广告呼吁释放人质父亲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</link><description>这些广告包括电视、广播和广告牌广告，总理办公室称这些广告的观看次数已达 1000 万次，将在全国观看超级碗比赛时在美国媒体上播放</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>